thread.title_full: Biden calls Paul Ryan 'good guy,' hopes for progress with Congress - Worldnews.com

author: wn.com
title: Biden calls Paul Ryan 'good guy,' hopes for progress with Congress
text: WASHINGTON (Reuters) - Vice President Joe Biden, calling former campaign opponent Paul Ryan a "good guy," voiced hope in an interview that the White House could make progress with Congress on the budget and other issues if Ryan becomes House of Representatives speaker.
